{"about_the_game":"CAPTURED is an analog horror game where you capture anomalies on camera to escape what seems to be an endless hallway in your own home. Investigate mysterious phenomena, survive frightening entities, and reach the end of the hallway!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam1_00000.png?t=1737386838\" /><br>Explore a procedural generated endless hallway filled with unusual phenomena and ever-changing rooms. Caught in a never-ending loop, leaving the house only leads you right back into the same hallway. Plunged in complete darkness, room after room, your once-familiar home feels increasingly alien.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam_2.gif?t=1737386838\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam3_00000.png?t=1737386838\" /><br>Break the loop by exercising your memory skills. Use your camera to zoom in on suspicious changes and select their anomaly type. Missing or incorrectly identifying any unusual phenomena within a loop will wipe your camera's memory. Correctly capture 13 anomalies to escape.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam4.gif?t=1737386838\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam5_00000.png?t=1737386838\" /><br>Watch out for unwanted company. While silence may be a good tactic, staying too long within a loop could give away your location. Use your flashlight, camera, and the doors strategically to survive each entity's unique mechanics.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam_9.gif?t=1737386838\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/steam7_00000.png?t=1737386838\" /><br>Using a custom movement experience, step into a nostalgic late '90s aesthetic with realistic graphics, minimal UI, and a chilling atmosphere.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam7.gif?t=1737386838\" /><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience isolation and the eerie feeling of being trapped in a looping house set in the late 90s.<br></li><li>Explore a procedurally generated hallway filled with a chilling atmosphere.<br></li><li>Use your camera to zoom in on anomalies and capture them.<br></li><li>Identify and classify captured anomalies, including Object, Electronic, Lighting, Water, Missing Room, and Deformed Room.<br></li><li>Survive encounters with three monsters, each with unique traits and mechanics.<br></li><li>Immerse yourself in an analog horror experience featuring realistic graphics, a VHS 90s aesthetic, a dynamic camera system, and immersive flashlight movement.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"He's a hugger!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/e235e02dd80ae4d10007fead79dbef191390a4b5.jpg"},{"name":"Don't stare too long...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/bd48020329e4afa5621e2aca4216d17dad6edf49.jpg"},{"name":"Feeling blue?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/23507ee86e68a241f9b16e47ab7e7ac2fcb50aa0.jpg"},{"name":"One too many legs!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/c5f26f3109a59f3206e5b061819cbe29df1e4f23.jpg"},{"name":"It's a loop!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/5bb5d5f3ddf54abf891d568f31e25380b8d3ead2.jpg"},{"name":"AVOID HIM!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/2fa700560c440d6d1db6ea4d59ebb81e14f88de8.jpg"},{"name":"Beyond The Loop","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/33cda4c072cc14e38ef6d866359b2cac6cb71828.jpg"},{"name":"Hard Core Escape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/146e0adfc09dc61dca087c8531591cb173333f7e.jpg"},{"name":"Die-hard Observer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/ee9e3b842b9ecd34078c65cfeb22320caeecd7c4.jpg"},{"name":"Unexplained Disappearances ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3114010/369df7227ea779905ca5be8301ef59ada4e1e278.jpg"}],"total":12},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737386838","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/page.bg.jpg?t=1737386838","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737386838","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737386838","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"CAPTURED is an analog horror game where you capture anomalies on camera to escape what seems to be an endless hallway in your own home. Investigate mysterious phenomena, survive frightening entities, and reach the end of the hallway!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114010/extras/Steam1_00000.png?t=1737386838\" /><br>Explore a procedural generated endless hallway filled with unusual phenomena and ever-changin